locality: Kitulo National Park, Northern Livingstone Mountains, Bujingijila Village.
Mamiwa North Forest Reserve, Mkobwe area along road to Nongwe Village.

7 km from S of Ruanda II (approximately 2 km N of water tank at Ilembo on Ilembo - Mbalizi road). In Mbogo Forest Reserve (Umalila), in mixed forest and on brushy south-facing slopes.
